The paper deals with real-time embedded systems and schedulability analysis, which are typically studied in the sub-categories of Operating Systems (cs.OS), Real-Time Systems (cs.RT), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Programming Languages (cs.PL). The paper's abstract mentions the analysis of different task models and scheduling algorithms, which further supports the likelihood of these sub-categories.
